<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.8">
<l>ēṉa mīṉā maiyō ṭariyuñ ciṟukuṟaḷumāy</l>
<l>tāṉu māyat taraṇit talaiva ṉiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>vāṉum maṇṇum niṟaiyap pukuntīṇ ṭivaṇaṅkunal</l>
<l>tēṉum pāluṅ kalantaṉ ṉavarcērt teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place of the leader of the world who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become a lion and a little dwarf,</l>
<l>Along with a boar, fish, and tortoise, became himself,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South where gather those of heaven and earth to worship,</l>
<l>Entering in hordes so [they] fill [the temple],</l>
<l rend="indent">mixing like fine honey and milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
